#: ../../../gpu/todo.rst:935
msgid ""
"drm_sched_resubmit_jobs() is deprecated. Main reason being that it leads to "
"reinitializing dma_fences. See that function's docu for details. The better "
"approach for valid resubmissions by amdgpu and Xe is (apparently) to figure "
"out which job (and, through association: which entity) caused the hang. "
"Then, the job's buffer data, together with all other jobs' buffer data "
"currently in the same hardware ring, must be invalidated. This can for "
"example be done by overwriting it. amdgpu currently determines which jobs "
"are in the ring and need to be overwritten by keeping copies of the job. Xe "
"obtains that information by directly accessing drm_sched's pending_list."
msgstr ""

